title: Playboy's Book of Lingerie - 90s - Pictures selection
description:
These pictures are THOSE I SELECTED from the Playboy's Book of Lingerie magazines (PDFs), from 1984 (first edition) to 2002 --- Mainly the 90s.


- Number of pictures:  648

- Size: 	178.539.490 bytes

- Format: 	All JPEG, except 4 PNG and 8 PPM

- Image quality:
They are the original size and quality of what the PDFs contained.
Some pictures are small, some are big (max. 1600px).
As those magazines are quiet old and in PDF format, don't expect high resolution quality.


Enjoy !
